{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a1ee52b94f","title":"给毛宇居的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f76b8dc17c","index":0,"year":1952,"month":10,"day":2,"articleId":"a1ee52b94f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"ff2581c942","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛宇居，毛泽东的堂兄和少年时的私垫老师。"},{"id":"58b8abc2a2","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李，指李激清，辛亥革命前是韶山的进步教员，毛泽东常去他家看书、请教。邹，指邹普勋，毛泽东少年时的私熟同学和邻居。"},{"id":"e12b4961e0","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽连，毛泽东的堂弟。"},{"id":"b804a5e187","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"泽荣，即毛泽荣，又名逊五，毛泽东的堂弟。"}],"contents":[{"id":"92987461c5","type":"title","text":"给毛字居的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"ff2581c942","type":"paragraph","text":"宇居兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"58b8abc2a2","type":"paragraph","text":"李邹二位来京，收到你的信，并承佳观，甚为感谢","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"e12b4961e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽连以来信叫苦，母尚未葬，脚又未好，兹寄人民币三百万元，以一百万元为六师葬费，二百万元为泽连治病之费。请告他不要来京，可到长沙湘雅医院诊治，如湘雅诊不好，北京也就诊不好了。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"b804a5e187","type":"paragraph","text":"另寄二百万元给泽荣（逊五）助其家用。他有信来，我尚未复，请转告他，不另写信了。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"df9fb1c2cf","type":"paragraph","text":"以上均请费神转致为荷！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"2fdd8e6fab","type":"subtitle","text":"顺问","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"ac40d49e8d","type":"paragraph","text":"康吉！","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"b3f9639726","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"38621e78a6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年十月二日","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"},{"id":"76cba5be27","type":"paragraph","text":"这些钱均是我自己的稿费，请告他们节用。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f"}],"page":{"id":"c089244381","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a1ee52b94f","start":276,"end":276}}}},"__N_SSG":true}